panels.description:
Status of the job on the cluster:         
*Stopped*: Current status is stopped     
*Started*: The dagger has restarted once or more during the selected time interval
*Running*: The dagger is running fine for the duration selected
panels.title: Status

panels.description: The time that the job ran/running since the last restart
panels.title: Runtime since last restart

panels.description: The configured sink type for dagger

targets.query: select last("sink_type") as output_sink from (select "sink_type","value" from "taskmanager_job_task_operator_sink_type_value" WHERE $timeFilter AND  "job_name" =~ /^$Jobs$/)

panels.title: Sink

panels.description: The total number of full restarts since this job was submitted
panels.title: Full restarts

panels.description:
For jobs currently in a restarting situation, the time elapsed during this outage.
Returns 0 for running jobs
panels.title: Total downtime

panels.description:
The maximum lag in terms of number of records for any partition in this window. An increasing value over time is your best indication that the consumer group is not keeping up with the producers. This is for each task.           
1 <= Number of task <=  parallelism
panels.title: Max kafka consumer lag

panels.description:
The number of records a task has dropped due to arriving late.             
1 <= Number of task <=  parallelism
panels.title: Late Records Dropped per 5 minutes

panels.description:
This gives an idea of data flow through tasks.    
Input: The number of records a task receives per second.
Output: The number of records a task sends per second.                           
1 <= Number of task <=  parallelism

targets.query: SELECT mean("rate") FROM "taskmanager_job_task_operator_numRecordsInPerSecond" WHERE ("job_name" =~ /^$Jobs$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1m), "subtask_index" fill(0)
SELECT mean("rate") FROM "taskmanager_job_task_operator_numRecordsOutPerSecond" WHERE ("job_name" =~ /^$Jobs$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1m), "subtask_index" fill(0)

panels.title: Records Rate - All Stages
